<HEADLINE>
<P>
POP MUSIC SPECIAL; 
</P>
<P>
THE RECORD INDUSTRY'S BIG PUSH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Craig Lee 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The fall season is always the most active time for pop record releases, as the 
music industry gears up for its November-December season, during which nearly a 
third of all records, tapes and CDs are sold. But that can mean confusion for 
