Photo, Cue cards in Spanish aid actors during scene in Spanish-language Star 
Trek adventure at Universal Studios. Shows are part of park's effort to attract 
Latino customers. CARLOS CHAVEZ / L.A. Times; Photo, Bertah Flores dons costume 
for her role in Spanish-language Star Trek show at Universal Studios. ; Photo, 
Spanish-language crew of the starship Enterprise shows how the magic is created 
at Universal Studios. CARLOS CHAVEZ / L.A. Times 
</P>
