Coast Conference cross-country meet at Belmont, Calif. Portland won both team 
titles. Portland's Matt Sabo was the men's individual winner, running the 
10-kilometer course in 33:02. Three Loyola freshmen had a strong pack finish, 
with Eric Merk placing 18th in 36:41, followed by Mike Thom 19th (36:43) and 
Kevin Delaney 20th (36:52). 
</P>
