<HEADLINE>
<P>
SAVAGING REV. MARTIN LUTHER KING JR.'S REPUTATION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
It is interesting to note that Ralph David Abernathy is vice-president of the 
board of directors of the American Freedom Coalition, one of the most 
ferociously right-wing, allegedly Moonie-backed groups that currently exists in 
the United States. 
</P>
<P>
Is his biography of the Rev. Martin Luther King Jr. truly a quest for truth, or 
is it one more attempt to discredit those men and women who fight for the civil 
liberties of the disenfranchised? 
</P>
<P>
VIRGINIA URIBE, Los Angeles 
</P>
