<P>
WORLD SERIES; BASEBALL PLAYERS; SAN FRANCISCO GIANTS (BASEBALL TEAM); OAKLAND 
A'S (BASEBALL TEAM); CRAIG, ROGER (BASEBALL PLAYER) 
</P>
