<SUBJECT>
<P>
MIDDLE EAST PEACE; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- ISRAEL; ISRAEL -- 
REVOLTS; ISRAEL -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- PLO; SHAMIR, YITZHAK 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
