CRIME; MERCER, LEONARD J JR; RESTAURANTS -- FLORIDA; TEAMSTERS UNION; HIGGINS, 
JOSEPH J; OMNI FUNDING GROUP INC; KICKBACKS; PERJURY; LOANS 
</P>
