<HEADLINE>
<P>
WORKER INJURIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Source: Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Here are some statistics on worker safety and production provided by the 
National Safety Council, the National Safe Workplace Institute, the Institute 
for Southern Studies, the United Food and Commercial Workers Union, the United 
Autoworkers Union and federal government agencies. 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
Injuries, all Industries (per 100 Full-Time Workers) 
</P>
<TABLE CWL="1.56IN:3.32IN:3.21IN" WDM="ABS" NCOLS="3">
<ROWRULE>  </ROWRULE>
